{"tid":2270869,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"設計師被控襲兩警 辯方質疑認錯人","createTime":"2020-11-04T09:01:51.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-04T09:32:53.000Z","uid":56115,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"c94af62e8982f84328e150752cdacff465dab4b9","tid":2270869,"uid":56115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-04T09:01:51.000Z","msg":"去年9月1日網民發起「和你飛2.0」，有示威者堵塞機場及多區交通。當晚有設計師被指在坑口襲擊總督察及警署警長，遭控兩項襲警罪，案件今日在觀塘裁判法院開審。辯方質疑總督察追截被告的路段「九曲十三彎」，而且燈光忽明忽暗，可能有「認錯人」之嫌。總督察在盤問下承認自己未能清晰量化雙方距離，但多次重申<span class=\"red\">被告一直在他的視線範圍內</span>。<br />\n<br />\n總督察丁家豪今供稱，當晚坑口港鐵站附近有示威者聚集，有人向警方照射雷射光，他於是帶領小隊上前驅散。<span class=\"red\">其間他見一名女子跌倒，他欲上前扶起時</span>，被告突然從左前方衝出，用雨傘兩度向他揮打。"},{"pid":"c49682f5cda984665bb73e46863aeb034b3e57ec","tid":2270869,"uid":56115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-04T09:02:53.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201104/TH6VOAPEP5C3LMSBUYE7YINDDQ/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201104%2FTH6VOAPEP5C3LMSBUYE7YINDDQ%2F&d=O3JFyT0uW1vU8ssvO3VcykYzBSotcsoJ75UENuGtOl4%3D&h=197f29e0\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201104%2FTH6VOAPEP5C3LMSBUYE7YINDDQ%2F&h=229dce52\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201104/TH6VOAPEP5C3LMSBUYE7YINDDQ/</a>"},{"pid":"bcca5989624ee3127a348c2ee2622cfb714a874d","tid":2270869,"uid":56115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-11-04T09:04:52.000Z","msg":"鳩UP咬人話自己去扶個女人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ad652fc5bfaa949b6db463cc541b5e1734ab73a8","tid":2270869,"uid":56115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-04T09:13:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a23f438d60b3bdc304c836d